Context: New Paramount Studios is retained by the Student Association at George Brown College. It is open for graduating students and offers photograph sessions at the Waterfront and Casa Loma campuses, as well as their studios in Toronto and Mississauga. Appointments must be booked before June 1, 2023, to be included in College Course Composites. New Paramount Studios provides graduation regalia for the photographs. For additional information, visit New Paramont's website (nps@look.ca) or the Student Association's grad photo page. The phone number for inquiries is 416-415-2000, and TTY is 1-877-515-5559. For college news, application deadlines, upcoming events, tours, and more, students can sign up on the website. Note: The information on this website may be subject to change without notice. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
